Scalability & Future Plan:

>>> Real-Time Healthcare Data Integration:

    Connect the dashboard to real-time healthcare or hospital databases for automatic updates and continuous monitoring of heart disease trends.

>>> Predictive Risk Analysis:

    Integrate machine learning models to predict heart disease risk probability based on factors such as age, BMI, diabetes, smoking, and lifestyle conditions.

>>> Advanced Filtering & Drill-Down Analysis:

    Add more advanced filters such as cholesterol levels, blood pressure, ECG results, and detailed BMI categories for deeper medical analysis.

>>> Deployment as Web-Based Healthcare Analytics Platform:

    Develop a web-based application to make the heart disease dashboard accessible to hospitals, researchers, and public health organizations.

>>>  Role-Based Access Dashboards:

     Create customized dashboard views for different stakeholders such as healthcare analysts, doctors, researchers, and policy makers to provide focused insights.
